cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with visual relationship detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also leverages linguistic knowledge to improve the performance of the model, which falls under natural language processing (cs.CL). The use of knowledge distillation is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG), and the paper also involves training a deep model (cs.AI). Finally, the experiments are conducted on visual datasets (cs.MM).
